t kind of law? "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or what principle?"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:31","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":31,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" By one of works? No, on the contrary, by a law "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or a principle"},{"kind":"text","text":" of faith. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 2:17","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":17},{"label":"Rm 2:23","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":23},{"label":"Rm 4:2","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":2},{"label":"1Co 1:29–31","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":29},{"label":"Rm 9:31","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":31}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or what principle?"},{"marker":2,"text":"Or a principle"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:3:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For we conclude that a person is justified by faith apart from the works of the law. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:39","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":39,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:31","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":31,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:9","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":9,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 2:20","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":20,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 2:24","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":24,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 2:26","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":26,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 13:39","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":39},{"label":"Rm 9:31","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":31},{"label":"Eph 2:9","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":9},{"label":"Jms 2:20","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":20},{"label":"Jms 2:24","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":24},{"label":"Jms 2:26","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":26}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:3:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Or is God the God of Jews only? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 10:34","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":34,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:24","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 10:12","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 15:9","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":9,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 3:28","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":28,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" Is he not the God of Gentiles too? Yes, of Gentiles too, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 10:34","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":34},{"label":"Rm 9:24","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":24},{"label":"Rm 10:12","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":12},{"label":"Rm 15:9","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":9},{"label":"Gl 3:28","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":28}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:3:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"since there is one God "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 10:12","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" who will justify the circumcised by faith "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 4:11","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 4:16","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 3:8","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":8,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the uncircumcised through faith. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 10:12","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":12},{"label":"Rm 4:11","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":11},{"label":"Rm 4:16","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":16},{"label":"Gl 3:8","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:3:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Do we then nullify the law through faith? Absolutely not! "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 20:16","book":"Luk","chapter":20,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 3:4","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" On the contrary, we uphold the law. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:17","b